snippet.title: Captains of the Wacky Waters - Steam Next Fest 2023 Demo
snippet.description:
Sail across the Wacky Waters to reach Heaven alive. Loot, shoot and defeat other captains as you find more crew members and upgrade your ship with new cannons and crazy gadgets. Sink. Repeat.

Captains of the Wacky Waters (C) Ceiling Games
Coming to Steam soon
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1571130/Captains_of_the_Wacky_Waters/
